要12%利息求市民放美金入去。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大耳窿咩？</span>你幾時聽過銀行會比12里架！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你依家個銀行體系玩撚袁架啦。唔驚死未自己放錢入去攞</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97c1694d34cdd7767df3b27838a1d82a16cdc1f","tid":1529970,"uid":272186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a0f4c02fde8b231eaef727f80b5a04018f2536d","tid":1529970,"uid":155292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ea3e9ccdde75f7288b5b23eced3489429d762313","tid":1529970,"uid":272186,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T00:20:57.000Z","msg":"如果真係熟economics會知撳錢嘅作用好細（因為香港有4萬億儲備，就算全世界最有錢嘅hedge fund都未必衝擊到），雖然作用唔大，但作為表態係唔錯選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[size=6]假如目標係要狙擊港元<br />\n真正方式應該係向銀行借入港元換美元<br />\n而唔係用自己既錢<br />\n假如同時間再沽期指進行雙邊操作<br />\n咁香港貨幣先叫做有可能被衝擊</strong>[size=6]"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"不過依家個問題係<br />\n如果啲儲備已經比大陸借走咗......?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:06:07.000Z","msg":"呢個都係估估下 無人知<br />\n就算借走/貨幣互換都係拎走部分，都係正常運作<br />\n<br />\n最大問題撳錢威力唔夠大 如果借埋錢去換美金作用就amplify <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9c39cb8a0a5f170537206f17e5679802874d44","tid":1529970,"uid":284559,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fingfx.thomsonreuters.com/gfx/mkt/12/5411/5361/3%20HK%20reserves%20monetary%20base%20aggregate%20balance.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffingfx.thomsonreuters.com%2Fgfx%2Fmkt%2F12%2F5411%2F5361%2F3%2520HK%2520reserves%2520monetary%2520base%2520aggregate%2520balance.png&h=05c5024a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBrown Brothers Harriman(BBH)分析師本月一篇報告指出，「如果中國內地武警進入香港，一切都沒得談了，」因為投資人的信心將被摧毀。<br />\n<br />\n不過，BBH認為不太可能出現這種最糟局面。但一些非官方跡象顯示，投資人已趕忙將資金匯出，地產仲介商稱香港民眾對馬來西亞、新西蘭及澳